<p><b>Futures studies</b>, <b>foresight</b>, or <b>futurology</b> is the <a href="/wiki/Science" title="Science">science</a>, <a href="/wiki/Art" title="Art">art</a> and practice of postulating possible, probable, and preferable <a href="/wiki/Future" title="Future">futures</a> and the worldviews and myths that underlie them. Futures studies (colloquially called "futures" by many of the field's practitioners) seeks to understand what is likely to continue, what is likely to change, and what is novel. Part of the discipline thus seeks a systematic and pattern-based understanding of past and present, and to determine the likelihood of future events and trends.<sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
